downloadTitle: Organizing shapes to create better diagrams in Visio 2010
downloadDescription: Learn how to organize the shapes in your Visio 2010 diagrams quickly and easily with built-in structured diagram shapes: containers, lists, and callouts.
detailsSection: Learn how to organize the shapes in your Microsoft Visio 2010 diagrams quickly and easily using structured diagrams. This white paper shows how structured diagrams—through containers, lists, and callouts—can help you capture and maintain the logical relationships between shapes in your diagrams with a lot less effort.
installInstructionSection: Click Download to view and save the document to your computer.
